

mafft --auto input_sequences.fasta > aligned_sequences.fasta
FastTree -nt -boot 1000 aligned.fasta > tree.nwk

There are two options to root and visualize a tree from .nwk file: 
  - the first and the easiest one is using MEGA X  
  - the second is using 'rooting_and_visual.py' script, which is better to launch in google colab
